data.meta_description: 29K likes, 481 comments - lenadunham on June 11, 2015: "Today my partner @jackantonoff released his new single Like A River Runs along with a gorgeous version sung by our friend Sia and a 15 minute spoken word piece about the nature of dreams. I am so proud of him, not just because he's a consummate artist who is always pushing himself and others into new creative territory but because he's a truly good man. Jack is a feminist who fights for equality, rejects injustice of all kinds and makes me feel safe by making sure I am always heard. He is my hero ❤️".
